IMAPAccount kzar
Host imap.fastmail.com
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
User kzar@kzar.co.uk
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only -d ~/code/davemail/.password.gpg"

IMAPStore kzar-remote
Account kzar

MaildirStore kzar-local
# The trailing "/" is important
Path ~/Maildir/
Inbox ~/Maildir/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel kzar
Master :kzar-remote:
Slave :kzar-local:
Patterns INBOX Travel Archive Sent Spam Trash
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Sync All

Channel kzar-quick
Master :kzar-remote:
Slave :kzar-local:
Patterns INBOX
SyncState *
Sync Pull New